Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'Evtx'

Solution: Install python-evtx: pip3 install python-evtx
Issue: Registry parsing fails with "Key not found"

Solution: Verify key path syntax uses backslashes. Check if key exists in hive using Registry.Registry(file).open(path)
Issue: PowerShell script execution fails

Solution: Ensure PowerShell Core is installed. Run with explicit path: pwsh -File script.ps1
Issue: JSON parsing errors in analysis

Solution: Validate JSON syntax. Check for incomplete extractions. Use jq to validate: jq . file.json
